text: National Highway 334DD, commonly referred to as NH 334DD is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 34. NH-334DD runs in the state of Uttar Pradesh in India. == Route == NH334DD connects Hamidpur, Jewar, Jhajhar, Kakod, Dhanaura and Bulandshahr in the state of Uttar Pradesh. == Junctions == : Terminal near Hamidpur. : Junction with Yamuna Expressway near Jewar : Terminal near Bulandshahar. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 334DD on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Uttar Pradesh
